Key Features
Visual States:
Idle (Tomoe): Deep red pulsing, waiting for input
Scanning: Spinning animation while detecting text
Processing (EMS Activating): Intensifying glow with progress bar
Active (EMS): Golden aura indicating translation overlay active
Error: Glitch effect with dark red tones
Offline: Dimmed, disabled appearance
Functionality:
Real-time health monitoring via Chrome extension messaging
Automatic retry logic with exponential backoff
Progress tracking for OCR/translation operations
Error logging with detailed diagnostics
Custom element API for easy integration (<status-indicator status="scanning" progress="45">)
Integration:
Dispatches statuschange and statusclick events
Responds to background script STATUS_UPDATE messages
Shadow DOM encapsulation for style isolation
Usage in popup.html:

<status-indicator id="mainStatus" status="idle"></status-indicator>
<script src="components/status-indicator.js"></script>